<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ق ح ل:</span> <span class="c2">(قَحَلَ)</span> الشَّيْءُ يَبِسَ وَبَابُهُ خَضَعَ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٤٨⦘ فَهُوَ <span class="c2">(قَاحِلٌ)</span> . وَ <span class="c2">(قَحِلَ)</span> مِنْ بَابِ طَرِبَ لُغَةٌ فِيهِ فَهُوَ <span class="c2">(قَحِلٌ)</span> . وَ <span class="c2">(قَحِلَ)</span> الشَّيْخُ <span class="c2">(قَحَلًا)</span> يَبِسَ جِلْدُهُ عَلَى عَظْمِهِ وَشَيْخٌ <span class="c2">(قَحْلٌ)</span> بِالتَّسْكِينِ وَ <span class="c2">(إِنْقَحْلٌ)</span> أَيْضًا بِكَسْرِ الْهَمْزَةِ أَيْ مُسِنٌّ جِدًّا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>